latestIgtvVideos.title: post quarantine
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Hahah ! So many possibilities of things that can happen post the quarintine ! 
So couples , my advice to u would be to spend the time u have together by doing things that u probably didn’t have much tome for earlier. Watch movies, make some of your favourite dishes together and take this time to understand more about each other ! 
For the bloggers and influencers and other artists , work on ur skill , practice your craft even thought you’re not going out to show them off ! 
And for all of us , do the things that we usually pile up for there ! It’s so much fun to do our things on Our own sometimes ! U would never know what ure capable of till u try them ! 
#quarintine2020 #day6lockdown #letsfightcoronavirus #stayhome #stayprotected

latestPosts.caption:
@iaanchalkhurana this is for you 
Tag ur that friend who needs to hear this

When two women stay together, they become each other’s rock, support, and strength 💪🌟 We were each other’s safe haven, our confidantes, and our forever friends 💕 We spent so much time together that we became each other’s pillow, our go-to person to share our joys and sorrows 🌟 But now, because of distance, work, or marriage, we have to be apart 💔 It’s a painful separation, and my heart aches for the bond we shared 💔 I miss our laughter, our talks, and our silly moments together 🌟 You’re more than just a friend to me; you’re my sister, my partner in crime, and my forever friend 💕
